structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 118, sec. 19, effective June 17, 1978. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 140, sec. 55. -- Amended 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 127. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 220, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Condemnation for any county or city for flood control purposes.
